    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300062348_5_5539-5610",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "5539-5610",
      "markText": "伯希和精通汉文，他用了三个星期的时间在藏经洞内翻检了所有的经卷，精心挑选出了学术价值极高的写卷6000多卷，以500两银子的价钱与王道士成交。",
      "totalCount": 702,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300062348&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=5539&rangeEnd=5610",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/7f0327d0813ab7edag018663?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=5539&rangeEnd=5610"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300062348_4_533-590",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "533-590",
      "markText": "敦煌位于中国甘肃省西部，河西走廊的最西端，西面是与塔克拉玛干大沙漠相接的库穆塔格沙漠，北面是戈壁，南面是祁连山脉。",
      "totalCount": 680,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300062348&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=533&rangeEnd=590",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/7f0327d0813ab7edag018663?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=533&rangeEnd=590"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300062348_3_463-555",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "463-555",
      "markText": "敦煌文化遗产包括三个方面的内容：一是敦煌地区的古代文化遗存，如汉代长城、汉简、各时代的出土文物等；二是以莫高窟为代表，包括西千佛洞、榆林窟等处的石窟；三是莫高窟藏经洞出土的数万件文物。",
      "totalCount": 672,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300062348&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=463&rangeEnd=555",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/7f0327d0813ab7edag018663?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=463&rangeEnd=555"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300062348_4_1313-1351",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "1313-1351",
      "markText": "到了唐代，石窟已达1000多座，于是这一片石窟被称为“莫高窟”，也叫千佛洞。",
      "totalCount": 640,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300062348&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1313&rangeEnd=1351",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/7f0327d0813ab7edag018663?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1313&rangeEnd=1351"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300062348_4_2156-2256",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "2156-2256",
      "markText": "就在张骞出使西域的同时，汉武帝对匈奴进行了一系列军事打击，占领了河西走廊，于公元前121年设置了酒泉、武威两郡。公元前111年又从两郡中分出张掖、敦煌两郡，历史上称为“河西四郡”，敦煌之名才得以问世。",
      "totalCount": 578,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300062348&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=2156&rangeEnd=2256",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/7f0327d0813ab7edag018663?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=2156&rangeEnd=2256"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300062348_4_20188-20242",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "20188-20242",
      "markText": "嘉靖三年（1524年），明朝政府放弃了包括敦煌在内的嘉峪关以外地区，封闭了嘉峪关，敦煌一带荒芜了近200年。",
      "totalCount": 560,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300062348&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=20188&rangeEnd=20242",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/7f0327d0813ab7edag018663?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=20188&rangeEnd=20242"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300062348_4_2281-2312",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "2281-2312",
      "markText": "汉朝在敦煌城西设立了阳关和玉门关，敦煌郡便成了中国西面的门户。",
      "totalCount": 528,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300062348&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=2281&rangeEnd=2312",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/7f0327d0813ab7edag018663?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=2281&rangeEnd=2312"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300062348_4_12171-12198",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "12171-12198",
      "markText": "当时的元宵灯会，号称“长安第一，敦煌第二，扬州第三”。",
      "totalCount": 476,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300062348&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=12171&rangeEnd=12198",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/7f0327d0813ab7edag018663?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=12171&rangeEnd=12198"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300062348_4_5821-5840",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "5821-5840",
      "markText": "白马寺就是正史上记载的中国最早的寺庙。",
      "totalCount": 468,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300062348&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=5821&rangeEnd=5840",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/7f0327d0813ab7edag018663?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=5821&rangeEnd=5840"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300062348_4_20358-20456",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "20358-20456",
      "markText": "明代以后的敦煌石窟艺术几乎是空白，清代虽然也对莫高窟、榆林窟做了很多修复工作，然而，由于文化传承的断裂、传统技艺的丧失，已无法与前代的任何时期相比。所以，一般来说，敦煌石窟的艺术史到元代便告结束。",
      "totalCount": 442,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300062348&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=20358&rangeEnd=20456",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/7f0327d0813ab7edag018663?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=20358&rangeEnd=20456"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300062348_5_3176-3257",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "3176-3257",
      "markText": "而实际上王道士成了这个宝库的直接管理者，他不断地偷偷弄出一些古写本送人或估价出售。就这样，由于清廷的黑暗、地方政府的麻木，造成了中国文化史上这一幕触目惊心的悲剧。",
      "totalCount": 435,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300062348&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=3176&rangeEnd=3257",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/7f0327d0813ab7edag018663?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=3176&rangeEnd=3257"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300062348_5_7512-7605",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "7512-7605",
      "markText": "现藏俄罗斯的敦煌经卷达1万多卷。虽然有不少是碎片，但这个数目也是非常惊人的。由于资料不详，我们无法弄清楚为什么在中国政府已经把剩余的敦煌写卷送到北京以后，俄国探险队还能得到这么多的写卷。",
      "totalCount": 396,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300062348&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=7512&rangeEnd=7605",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/7f0327d0813ab7edag018663?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=7512&rangeEnd=7605"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300062348_5_9188-9260",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "9188-9260",
      "markText": "这伙绝望潦倒的士兵冲着壁画任意发泄，在精美的壁画上乱写乱画。由于他们在一些洞内生火做饭，部分洞窟遭到前所未有的烟熏污染，无数的艺术珍品遭受破坏。",
      "totalCount": 396,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300062348&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=9188&rangeEnd=9260",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/7f0327d0813ab7edag018663?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=9188&rangeEnd=9260"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300062348_5_21591-21637",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "21591-21637",
      "markText": "著名敦煌学家季羡林先生提出了“敦煌在中国，敦煌学在世界”的口号，指出了将来敦煌学发展的方向。",
      "totalCount": 392,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300062348&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=21591&rangeEnd=21637",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/7f0327d0813ab7edag018663?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=21591&rangeEnd=21637"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300062348_4_17953-18022",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "17953-18022",
      "markText": "尽管曹氏不遗余力地营建洞窟，但这一时期的绘画着色单调、绘制简陋、创造力衰退，千篇一律的倾向很明显，表现出经济力量的衰弱以及文化上的封闭性。",
      "totalCount": 360,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300062348&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=17953&rangeEnd=18022",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/7f0327d0813ab7edag018663?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=17953&rangeEnd=18022"
    },
